title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Edible Prepar
description: Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Edible Prepar in the United Kingdom decreased to 225.53 GBP Million in September from 239.13 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Edible Prepar in the United Kingdom averaged 125.76 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 266.43 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 40.54 GBP Million in January of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Edible Prepar.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
